e\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(132,72,'interviewee_title','Freelance Photographer'),(133,72,'_interviewee_title','field_4f52f4ea9f5fb'),(134,72,'summary','Eighteen months ago, Australian-born photographer Glen Allsop was whisked away from his beach-bum lifestyle in suburban Sydney and cast out on the mean streets of NYC in a career move that’s seen him shoot some of the world’s most spectacular destinations. Working under the Christian Oth Studio banner, Glen attributes his success as a wedding photographer to his ability to encompass the roles of photojournalist<!--more-->, editorial shooter and party snapper all at once, while - most importantly - being a nice guy.  On top of that, Glen has been quietly building his street-style portfolio since his move to the Big Apple, documenting the city’s best dressed and indulging his other big passion: luxury cars. One thing\'s for sure, this guy is no one-trick pony.'),(135,72,'_summary','field_4f52f5c0b695a'),(136,72,'links',''),(137,72,'_links','field_4f52f8762087b'),(138,72,'state','featured'),(139,72,'_state','field_4f52f8ae74b69'),(140,72,'feature_image','157'),(141,72,'_feature_image','field_4f52fa7e37fbf'),(142,2,'_edit_lock','1333128064:1'),(143,2,'_edit_last','1'),(144,80,'_edit_last','1'),(169,2,'recommended_links_0_link_text','TSN'),(170,2,'_recommended_links_0_link_text','field_4f539e36a264d'),(171,2,'recommended_links_0_link_address','http://tsn.ca'),(172,2,'_recommended_links_0_link_address','field_4f539e4a66ada'),(173,2,'recommended_links_1_link_text','ESPN'),(146,80,'allorany','all'),(178,80,'rule','a:4:{s:5:\"param\";s:4:\"page\";s:8:\"operator\";s:2:\"==\";s:5:\"value\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"order_no\";s:1:\"0\";}'),(148,80,'position','normal'),(149,80,'layout','default'),(150,80,'show_on_page','a:6:{i:0;s:11:\"the_content\";i:1;s:13:\"custom_fields\";i:2;s:10:\"discussion\";i:3;s:8:\"comments\";i:4;s:4:\"slug\";i:5;s:6:\"author\";}'),(151,80,'_edit_lock','1330880484:1'),(153,80,'field_4f539aef6569a','a:9:{s:3:\"key\";s:19