rom there on out we were able to get corporate contracts from Lamborghini, Bentley, Rolls Royce, Bugatti and many many more contracts from the distributors directly. We also have current contracts with major sporting teams and their league offices. I\'m George Sukunyan, the founder and president/CEO of the company.</p>\n\n<div><img class=\"left\" src=\"http://iandi.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/jplogistics1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"380\" /></div>\n<div class=\"caption left\">SVSV Our Hyper Reality Collection 2011</div>\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nHow many people currently work for JP logistics inc.?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nWe have over 50 employees world wide.\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nObviously you have a personal passion for high performance vehicles, at what age did you decide that the luxury auto industry was the career you wanted to pursue?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nI have been around vehicles all my life. My dad is the biggest influence for vehicles, and now my younger brother Arman Sukunyan who is currently in college is a bigger car nut than both of us. He also learning the art of Logistics to take over company operations after he graduates.\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nWhat are some of your personal vehicles?\n<h3 class=\"answer clear-left\">George:</h3>\nBeing in the line of work I am, I have previously owned and currently own some heavy metal. From a Lamborghini to a Nissan GTR Hennessey edition # 001. My favorite vehicles are my classics. I have an all original 1957 Chevy Belair, the vehicle only had 2 owners when purchased. I use it as my Sunday beach car during the summer. I also own a 1949 Mercury Custom chopped vehicle built from the ground up by my dad Joe Sukunyan, and our current project is a 1947 Ford COE truck.\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nWhat is your favorite super car and have you had a chance to drive it?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nMy Favorite super car is the ultimate one that every person would love to drive but only some get lucky enough to see it. The Bugatti SuperSport is the ultimate car of choice, I have been fortunate enough not only to drive it but also drive it on the race track. It is just an amazing machine with so much power, control and speed.\n<h3 class=\"question clear-left\">Asher:</h3>\nHow many locations do you have throughout the world and where are you looking to expand to?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\n<p class=\"spacer\">Our import/export division has 6 offices throughout the World and we have 4 offices in Los Angeles. We can also proudly state that we have over 120 sister companies that we have contracts with across the world to use their location for our valuable customer to drop off or pick up their vehicles.</p>\n<img class=\"full-width\" src=\"http://iandi.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/jplogistics2.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n<div class=\"caption full-width\">SVSV Our Hyper Reality Collection 2011</div>\n<h3 class=\"question clear-left\">Asher:</h3>\nJP logistics inc has a large custom fleet of trucks and trailers, what are some of the special features of these and what helps to ensure safe travel for the vehicles?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nAll of our equipments have a live GPS tracking system, not only do we track the travel and location but we make sure all of our drivers are well rested, and ready for the great American roads. All of our trucks and trailers are maintained on a daily basis mechanically and physically. We take pride in our equipment as it shows who we are. We have our own in house mechanics at every terminal of ours across the Nation.\n<div class=\"three-column line-3-after\">\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nOn a typical day, how many vehicles does JP Logistics transport?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nOn a daily basis we move anywhere from 15 to 17 vehicles. Annually we book over 4000 plus orders and some orders are 5 to 10 vehicles at a time.\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nThere must be some great perks to this job, what are some of them?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nThe great perks of the job are too many to list, however the best part is being around so many beautiful vehicles. We also have the privilege of meeting some of the greatest people across the world, from governments and celebrities to athletes and Billionaires.\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nWho are some of the people you have had the opportunity to meet?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nI have met the likes of Steve Jobs, President Ronald Reagan, Vladimir Putin, Kobe Bryant, Danica Patrick, Dale Earnhardt (SR &amp; JR), Steve Wynn and Lebron James... the list is endless.\n<div>\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nThere are some big things coming up for JP Logistics this year, can you share some of them?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nI wish I could, but lets just say we have a very big surprise for our fans and followers. Something that has not been done in the industry. Some of our competitors already have an idea of what it is and they are not liking it.\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nWhat are some of the main things that make your company the best at what it does?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nOur customer service and our personal commitment, from our receptions to our dispatchers and drivers. We make sure that every customer is satisfied. I myself will answer calls and talk to the clients to make sure they are happy from A to Z.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div><img class=\"right\" src=\"http://iandi.spiraldesign.ca/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/jplogistics3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"380\" /></div>\n<div class=\"caption right\">SVSV Our Hyper Reality Collection 2011</div>\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nOut of all of the luxury cars your company gets to transport... what are the ones that still amaze you when you see and hear them?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nBugatti and Koenigsegg\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nAs a CEO of a successful company, what is your favorite part of running JP Logistics Inc.?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\nHaving great conversations about vehicles with our customers. From the young kid that has just bought their dream car to the race car drivers that just finished the race and want to share the vehicle performance.\n<h3 class=\"question\">Asher:</h3>\nLamborghini or Ferrari?\n<h3 class=\"answer\">George:</h3>\n<p class=\"spacer\">Its a tough one, but I can tell you this... Ferrari for everyday driving and a Lamborghini for the Rally\'s and weekends. I will also say that the new Lamborghini LP700 is my current favorite vehicle between Ferrari and Lamborghini.</p>','GEORGE SUKUNYAN','','inherit','open','open','','103-autosave','','','2012-03-26 11:21:50','2012-03-26 18:21:50','',103,'http://iandi.spiraldesign.ca/103-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(31,1,'2012-03-04 04:52:27','2012-03-04 04:52:27','','Interview Custom Fields','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_interview-custom-fields','','','2012-03-29 17:13:01','2012-03-30 00:13:01','',0,'http://spiraldesign.ca/?post_type=acf&#038;p=31',0,'acf','',0),(35,1,'2012-03-04 04:55:14','2012-03-04 04:55:14','','Interview Custom Fields','','inherit','open','open','','acf_interview-custom-fields','','','2012-03-04 04:55:14','2012-03-04 04:55:14','',31,'http://spiraldesign.ca/?p=35',0,'revision','',0),(38,1,'2012-03-04 05:05:38','2012-03-04 05:05:38','','Interview Custom Fields','','inherit','open','open','','acf_interview-custom-fields-2','','','2012-03-04 05:05:38','2012-03-04 05:05:38','',31,'http://spiraldesign.ca/?p=38',0,'revision','',0),(40,1,'2012-03-04 05:08:59','2012-03-04 05:08:59','','Interview Custom Fields','','inherit','open','open','','acf_interview-custom-fields-3','','','2012-03-04 05:08:59','2012-03-04 05:08:59','',31,'http://spiraldesign.ca/?p=40',0,'revision','',0),(42,1,'2012-03-04 05:11:55','2012-03-04 05:11:55','','Interview Custom Field